==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Excepting
<hw>Ex*cept"ing</hw>, <pos>prep. & conj.</pos>, but properly a
<pos>participle</pos>. <def>With rejection or exception of; excluding;
except.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Excepting</xex> your worship's
presence.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>No one was ever yet made utterly miserable, <qex>excepting</qex>
by himself.</q> <rj><qau>Lubbock.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Exception</ent>⟦br⟧
